headline: What Catalysts Are Shaping the Evolving Narrative for IQVIA Holdings?
summary: IQVIA Holdings has recently seen its consensus analyst price target rise significantly, climbing from $223.42 to $246.84. This upward revision reflects increased analyst confidence, due to the company’s workforce stability, competitive business-to-business performance, and strategic diversification across technology and analytics.
